147
00:07:59,916 --> 00:08:03,646
And if you have a single
machine, this works great.


148
00:08:04,036 --> 00:08:05,156
The cert is created.


149
00:08:05,156 --> 00:08:08,356
You have a private key that's
generated, and it stays


150
00:08:08,356 --> 00:08:10,296
in your keychain
and it just works.


151
00:08:11,236 --> 00:08:14,556
Now what happens if
you have a second Mac?


152
00:08:15,056 --> 00:08:17,926
Well, to build and sign
on that second Mac,


153
00:08:18,426 --> 00:08:20,896
