private key on the second Mac.


156
00:08:30,226 --> 00:08:32,796
Or you can create a new
signing certificate.


157
00:08:33,246 --> 00:08:35,905
But that first requires
getting rid of the old one.


158
00:08:36,635 --> 00:08:39,816
And now you can build on the
second Mac, but you can't build


159
00:08:39,816 --> 00:08:41,035
on your first Mac anymore.


160
00:08:41,635 --> 00:08:44,836
And it's easy to repeat this
process, and go back and forth


161
00:08:44,836 --> 00:08:47,946
between being able to build on
one machine, and not being able


162
00:08:47,946 --> 00:08:49,116
to build on another one.


163
00:08:49,116 --> 00:08:51,956
