00:26:46,116 --> 00:26:48,976
I'll select it and click, Edit.


531
00:26:49,456 --> 00:26:51,306
And I can scroll down
through all of this.


532
00:26:51,306 --> 00:26:54,656
I'm not making changes
to certs or to devices.


