00:27:31,396 --> 00:27:34,056
This is provisioning profile
specifier working behind


547
00:27:34,056 --> 00:27:34,526
the scenes.


548
00:27:35,116 --> 00:27:37,226
Once I installed the new
version of the profile,


549
00:27:37,726 --> 00:27:40,056
Xcode just started
using it automatically.


550
00:27:40,876 --> 00:27:43,296
Now I can build and run
the free version of my app,


551
00:27:43,836 --> 00:27:44,836
and everything will work.


552
00:27:44,836 --> 00:27:46,176
I can use iCloud and Push.


